<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5f6e23708f0e888ccda2a606ef9fd4a1>.
<#5f6e23708f0e888ccda2a606ef9fd4a1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/a71f56f5-da58-476d-8866-67937e260b4f>;
