<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/aaaff2d2-c58b-4aa5-88af-565eb5f3d6d5> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__375
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#63ece687d0211f4127404ea02f2919b7>.
<#63ece687d0211f4127404ea02f2919b7> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
