<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0435867aa9d16b13b72aebffce06cd7d>.
<#0435867aa9d16b13b72aebffce06cd7d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/fa574631-e811-48c7-afa6-fd402815b4eb>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-09T06:44:24.351Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#0435867aa9d16b13b72aebffce06cd7d> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/fa574631-e811-48c7-afa6-fd402815b4eb> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "samhällsbyggnad", "nyckelkodsområde", "gis", "karta", "geodata", "map";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "fa574631-e811-48c7-afa6-fd402815b4eb";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "## Kartlager\n\nKartlager som visar delområden i Malmö kommun. Delområdena följer gränserna för Nyckelkodsområden IV-siffror. Områdena används främst för statistik. Kartlagret uppdateras vid behov av stadsbyggnadskontoret. Senaste uppdatering: september 2020.\n\n## Polygonlager\n\n__Koordinatsystem__  \n\nWGS84 (EPSG4326)\n\nSWEREF99 13 30 (EPSG3008)\n\n__Attributdata__  \n\nDelområdets namn: delomr\n\nDelområdets kod: do_kod \n\nDelområdets area: area\n\n(Resursen i TopoJSON-format har framgångsrikt använts vid geografisk datafördelning i Power BI.)"@sv, "## Map layers\n\nMap layer showing sub-areas in Malmö Municipality. The sub-areas follow the\nboundaries of Key Code Areas IV numbers. The areas are mainly used for\nstatistics. The map layer is updated as needed by the City Planning Office.\nLast update: September 2020.\n\n##  Polygon layer\n\n**Coordinate system**\n\nWGS84 (EPSG4326)\n\nSWEREF99 13 30 (EPSG3008)\n\n**Attribute data**\n\nSubarea name: subarea\n\nSubarea code: do_kod\n\nSub-area area: area\n\n(The TopoJSON format resource has been successfully used for spatial data\ndistribution in Power BI.)\n\n"@en, "## Kortlag\n\nKortlag, der viser delområder i Malmø Kommune. Delområderne følger grænserne\nfor Key Code Area IV-numrene. Områderne bruges primært til statistik.\nKortlaget opdateres efter behov af byplankontoret. Sidst opdateret: september\n2020.\n\n##  Polygonlag\n\n**Koordinatsystem**\n\nWGS84 (EPSG4326)\n\nSWEREF99 13 30 (EPSG3008)\n\n**Attributdata**\n\nNavn på delområde: delområde\n\nUnderområdekode: do_kod\n\nDelområde areal: område\n\n(TopoJSON-formatressourcen er blevet brugt med succes til distribution af\nspatiale data i Power BI.)\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__222.
_:b0__222 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/fa574631-e811-48c7-afa6-fd402815b4eb> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/bcbddb58c201e63da3e728b33a85afcc>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/fa574631-e811-48c7-afa6-fd402815b4eb/resource/24cc1d77-3760-46c8-b61c-a7ed99941e6a>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/fa574631-e811-48c7-afa6-fd402815b4eb/resource/5cae8fdc-b4a8-4791-87b9-94e41013f11b>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/fa574631-e811-48c7-afa6-fd402815b4eb/resource/b8959339-aef8-40dc-bffd-0e91b7cbbb34>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2021-01-12"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T14:52:12.164339"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Delområden"@sv, "Sub-areas"@en, "Delområder"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/SOCI>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#35d2e572a2437cd4bf3dc1342e95529a>.
