<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#f93190bd22fb92aa80ddcf1f0511c79b>.
<#f93190bd22fb92aa80ddcf1f0511c79b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-09T06:44:24.361Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#f93190bd22fb92aa80ddcf1f0511c79b> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "GIS", "Geodata", "Administrativ indelning", "Karta", "Map", "Stadsområde", "stadsområden";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/NEVER>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Kartlager som visar stadsområden i Malmö kommun. Stadsområden var en politiskt beslutad indelning baserad på stadsområdesförvaltningarnas\ngeografiska verksamhetsområde i staden. Indelningen gällde 2013 - 2017. För gällande geografisk indelning av staden hänvisas till delområden.\nKartlagret uppdateras inte. Senaste uppdatering: september 2020.\nPolygonlager"@sv, "Map layer showing urban areas in Malmö Municipality. Urban areas were a\npolitically decided division based on the geographical area of ​​operation of\nthe urban area administrations in the city. The division was valid from 2013\nto 2017. For the current geographical division of the city, reference is made\nto sub-areas. The map layer is not updated. Last update: September 2020.\nPolygon layer\n\n"@en, "Kortlag, der viser byområder i Malmø Kommune. Byområder var en politisk\nbesluttet opdeling baseret på det geografiske virkeområde for\nbyområdeforvaltningerne i byen. Opdelingen var gyldig fra 2013 til 2017. For\nden nuværende geografiske opdeling af byen henvises til delområder. Kortlaget\ner ikke opdateret. Sidst opdateret: september 2020. Polygonlag\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__317.
_:b0__317 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/590e717ed624870c5e5af379a019ac72>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/ff193dfb-fecb-49ba-bf93-efaef663e966>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/cb293f0c-72b5-4b17-a70a-1bb0b8671fff>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/368b0a2b-c6e5-4f86-81f4-48ebbf4a9301>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/3552b9ca-5d43-41cd-987f-c23b739101c0>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/a2d1274d-ed1b-4211-b950-322d98eabbf4>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/696b53d8-9d3c-4218-9253-a545f20bfecf>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/eb390606-f546-44fc-82c3-f04836c74e91>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/276d8ab5-18f6-4cf6-8d16-c947781388cc/resource/dd24a7b9-109b-449a-8aa0-cb52c758fdab>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-04-27"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
