<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/0f6029bd-15d1-4551-ba81-68f08aa2db48> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/ce429264a6a97cd4bc8687f7a5b0847d>;
