    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "ICOS ATC 14C Release analysed by ICOS CRL from Norunda (100.0 m), 2015-09-29–2025-01-21"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__8050.
