<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b3bb06865427c7fbd55f5e013319455a>.
<#b3bb06865427c7fbd55f5e013319455a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.23695/06J6-0J33>;
